items.badge_description: Round round get around, you get around. Get around round round you get around. Ooh-ooh! That’s 5 different beers from 5 different countries in a row.
Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 5 distinct venues!
You're exploring this great country the best way possible, one delicious beer at a time! That's one beer while in at least 5 states or countries.

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 5 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 2!
